invalid type: string "\n### Use Case Name:\nLog Course Access Behavior\n\n### Use Case ID:\n10\n\n### Description:\nLog events when learners enter and exit a course to analyze user count and\nusage duration within the course.\n\n### Actor:\nLearner\n\n### Pre-Condition:\n1. Learner is logged into the system.\n2. Learner is registered in the course .\n\n### Flow of Events:\nge\npermissions.\nĸĸĸĸĸĸ